    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You attack as the wind that carries the seeds of the next generation. Make a single attack. If it hits, it deals damage as normal and inflicts [sprout 1] on the creature. If the struck target was already sprouted, compare the attack roll -2 to the AC of a number of different targets within 15 feet of the initial target up to your initiation modifier. Repeat the damage and inflict [sprout 1] on all creatures struck by this second attack; this secondary attack does not spread further.</p>"
